{"tid":815694,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得成日坐飛機去海外睇event既人好自私?","createTime":"2018-09-12T08:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T09:20:17.000Z","uid":1678,"like":5,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5da484a0b206f8f1e4579c741468350f4c20d3","tid":815694,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:32:09.000Z","msg":"當人地做緊社畜既時候，佢地就自拍貼上網話玩得幾high<br />\n當香港event越做越差既時候，佢地就大無私樣咁去人地既地方睇event，番到黎就話人地個邊搞得有幾好，但根本無諗過想搞好香港既event<br />\n家陣香港無機會比你地班人睇event咩? 無地方比你打 call咩? 香港eventer有問題咩? 點解要成日走去海外人地既地方睇event同識朋友? 分明係太自大睇唔起自己身邊其他野，對自己既地方同人有偏見先成日走去人地既地方<br />\n有錢成日坐飛機既人根本唔應該睇event，因為佢地無辦法體會到窮人睇event既感受同辛酸"},{"pid":"9182fbca3e60c6bb521bdffed01c30e971128c9f","tid":815694,"uid":95991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194cdab5f0d767c0a4a55e226326d836a9232200","tid":815694,"uid":60736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:32:59.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball"},{"pid":"b3409a38ce784b12ee9189982c80f01e19687ddf","tid":815694,"uid":25769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<br />\n樓豬良波"},{"pid":"b770cd3c4b9deb69182244982e39765bcadf6deb","tid":815694,"uid":65155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"角"},{"pid":"2555d43d33bbbcf2e19e01ce147b3d3c7d736b89","tid":815694,"uid":202301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"人哋出去event 你都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6273544442b008fb6ce80a91d0b9706c4fff8036","tid":815694,"uid":198485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"酸"},{"pid":"a75668e6b03b691f54c39a1cd593c756a501904d","tid":815694,"uid":5721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"<i